    "Afterward, we have explored the enabling technologies underpinning large-scale agent collaboration, including capability discovery, dynamic task orchestration, adaptive communication protocols, consensus mechanisms, and incentive models.",
    "Finally, by identifying open challenges in scalability, interoperability, agent economics, security/privacy, and ethics, we have outlined a roadmap for future IoA research.",
    "As IoA continues to mature, sustained innovation in networking architectures, interoperability standards, and security paradigms will be essential to realize IoA ecosystems.Fig. 1.1Fig.",
